ely on ambiguity, which have been obtained in the five papers devoted\nto these parameters. We generalize some known results to any Abelian groups and\nwe more importantly derive many new results on these parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 Oct 2017 06:49:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Sep 2018 04:41:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-11"}
